      • scoreEdge

        private void scoreEdge(MapEdge edge,
             MapNode startPos,
             LocationEstimationVector LEV,
             int stepCount,
             double baseProb)
        Scoring an Edge with base Score and inserting it into the LEV
        Parameters:
        edge - the edge to be scored
        startPos - the StartNode the Edge is starting from
        LEV - the actual Location EstimationVector
        stepCount - the number of steps taht is needed basing on the map to get to the first step of the edge
        baseProb - the base Probability denotes the calculated probability for stepping to the first step on this edge.
